refactor: merge rebalance residuals endpoint into send-csv (Vercel 12-fn limit)

The standalone api/rebalance/residuals.js pushed the deployment to 13 serverless
functions, over the Hobby plan's limit of 12. Folded its load/upsert logic into
api/orderbook/send-csv.js as two new actions (rebalance-load-residuals /
rebalance-upsert-residuals) — same service-role helpers, same auth gate — and
deleted the standalone file. dashboard.html now calls the merged endpoint.

